quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  65,1,Ya eyyuhennebiyyu iza tallaktumunnisae fetallikuhunne liÂṀÄḟddetihinne ve ahsÄḟlÂṀÄḟddete vettekullahe rabbekum la tuhricuhunne min buyutihinne ve la yahrucne illa en yeÂṀtiyne bifahÄḟÅetin mubeyyinetin ve tilke hududullahi ve men yeteÂṀadde hududallahi fekad zaleme nefsehu la tedriy leÂṀallellahe yuhdisu baÂṀde zalike emren
  65,2,Feiza belaÄne ecelehunne feemsikuhunne bimaÂṀrufin ev farikuhunne bimaÂṀrufin ve eÅhidu zevey ÂṀadlin minkum ve ekÄḟymuÅÅehadete lillahi zalikum yuÂṀazu bihi men kane yuÂṀminu billahi velyevmilÂṀahÄḟri ve men yettekÄḟllahe yecÂṀal lehu mahrecen
  65,3,Ve yerzukhu min haysu la yahtesibu ve men yetevekkel ÂṀalellahi fehuve hasbuhu innallahe baliÄu emrihi kad ceÂṀalallahu likulli ÅeyÂṀin kadren
  65,4,Vellaiy yeisne minelmehÄḟydÄḟ min nisaikum inirtebtum feÂṀÄḟddetuhunne selasetu iÅhurin vellaiy lem yehÄḟdne ve ulatulÂṀahmali eceluhunne en yedaÂṀne hamlehunne ve men yettekÄḟllhe yecÂṀal lehu min emrihi yusren
  65,5,Zalike emrullahi enzelehu ileykum ve men yettekÄḟllahe yukeffir ÂṀanhu seyyiatihi ve yuÂṀzum lehu ecren
  65,6,Eskinuhunne min haysu sekentum min vucdikum ve la tudarruhunne litudayyiku ÂṀaleyhinne ve in kunne ulati hamlin feenfiku ÂṀaleyhinne hatta yedaÂṀne hamlehunne fein erdaÂṀne lekum featuhunne ucurehunne veÂṀtemiru beynekum bimaÂṀrufin ve in teÂṀasertum feseturdÄḟÂṀu lehu uhra
  65,7,LiyunfÄḟk zu seÂṀa tin min seÂṀatihi ve men kudire ÂṀaleyhi rizkuhu felyunfÄḟk mimma atahÄḟllahu la yukellifullahu nefsen illa ma ataha seyecÂṀalullahu baÂṀde ÂṀusrin yusren